00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.680
to meet you. This is an open space for the whole data science community to connect and

00:00:25.680 --> 00:00:30.719
chat about data science leadership, questions you're facing, and getting to learn about

00:00:30.719 --> 00:00:35.680
what's going on in the world of data across different industries. So each week we feature

00:00:35.680 --> 00:00:41.299
