00:01:20.919 --> 00:01:26.480
context. But we also have a Slido link where you can ask questions anonymously. And so

00:01:26.480 --> 00:01:32.320
I see Tyler and Hannah, thank you, both just shared that in the chat. But we share the

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:38.239
recordings of each session up to the Posit YouTube, so you can always go back and find

00:01:38.239 --> 00:01:44.800
helpful resources and see an overview of each week. And we also have a LinkedIn group for

00:01:44.800 --> 00:01:52.080
the Hangout, too, which I'll share in the chat here in just a second. One other note

00:01:52.080 --> 00:01:56.279
I wanted to add here in the beginning, too, is if anybody is hiring right now and wants

00:01:56.279 --> 00:02:01.519
to share that in the chat, feel free to put the link to the job descriptions there. I

00:02:01.519 --> 00:02:06.680
was going to share a link in a little bit later for Chase Carpenter, who is one of our

00:02:06.680 --> 00:02:14.199
featured leaders from the Chicago Cubs. They're hiring an assistant director of database marketing.

