00:05:51.519 --> 00:05:59.600
government. We just a few months ago announced we'd be using ARPA funding. So ARPA is American

00:05:59.600 --> 00:06:07.760
Rescue Plan Act. This is federal funding in response to COVID. Baltimore received about

00:06:07.760 --> 00:06:14.239
$640 million in ARPA funding, and we're using $2 million of that to create a digital services team.

00:06:14.880 --> 00:06:20.559
So that will be in my office. We've been recruiting. Our director of digital services,

00:06:20.559 --> 00:06:25.679
city's first director of digital services, just started on Monday. Their name is Shelby Switzer.

