They came from the Beck Center and from U.S. Digital Services. So really excited to have

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:36.640
them on board. I posted a link in the chat. We are still hiring for a couple of roles,

00:06:38.239 --> 00:06:46.880
lead developer and lead UX designer in particular. So if you're interested or know folks,

00:06:46.880 --> 00:06:54.959
please reach out, apply. And I can also talk a little bit about maybe some anticipated new roles

00:06:55.839 --> 00:07:02.079
later this year that would be in my office. Fingers crossed. But we can get to that as it

00:07:02.079 --> 00:07:09.600
comes up. So yeah, that's kind of a quick intro. Happy to take questions or yeah, however you all

00:07:09.600 --> 00:07:14.880
want to roll. Yeah. Awesome. And what about something you like to do in your free time too?

