Hi there. So I was, this is a, I guess a topical question for first session in January,

00:27:40.719 --> 00:27:49.520
it's goal setting season. So how, how do you balance, you know, it's a newish team. So how

00:27:49.520 --> 00:27:57.599
do you balance goals about, you know, setting up your shop and making, you know, your infrastructure

00:27:57.599 --> 00:28:05.760
great and easy to work with and the goals that are kind of, I guess the, the kind of higher up

00:28:05.760 --> 00:28:10.959
or your customers or your key stakeholders, the things they want, because I'm right in

00:28:10.959 --> 00:28:17.359
the middle of that dilemma and it's, it's tricky, right? Yeah, yeah, for sure.

00:28:20.959 --> 00:28:25.839
One is, I mean, if everything's a priority, nothing is a priority, but at least having

00:28:25.839 --> 00:28:31.439
