I'm kind of looking at some of my own, you know, like I said, so up until now I've been in office

00:28:39.760 --> 00:28:47.359
of one, so it's, it's in some ways, these are like the office OKRs and some ways they're like

00:28:47.359 --> 00:28:54.560
personal OKRs because I'm just one person, you know, but yeah, I mean, so in terms of the digital

00:28:54.560 --> 00:29:00.800
services team and onboarding and getting that just stood up, like, we're lucky enough that,

00:29:02.560 --> 00:29:06.400
you know, the mayor and city administrator needed to sign off on that, that spending

