00:44:59.600 --> 00:45:04.719
constrain them. We want to get them to use that data how they need to. So there's kind of a

00:45:04.719 --> 00:45:09.360
balancing act there where, like, yes, we need to be a little bit more constrained and a little bit

00:45:09.360 --> 00:45:17.600
more centralized with some things, but not at the cost of innovation, agency responsiveness,

00:45:18.479 --> 00:45:24.560
